<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7945c229-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s719l"><num value="719l">§ 719l.</num><heading> Antitrust laws</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter, and no action taken hereunder, shall imply or effect an amendment to, or exemption from, any provision of the antitrust laws.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7945c22a-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/94/586/s14">Pub. L. 94–586, § 14</ref>, <date date="1976-10-22">Oct. 22, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2915">90 Stat. 2915</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
